,"created_at":"2013-02-14t12:23:54z","updated_at":"2013-08-06t22:59:40z","closed_at":"2013-08-06t22:59:40z","pull_request":{"html_url":null,"diff_url":null,"patch_url":null},"body":"hello,\r\nexpected behaviour:\r\nwhen you press share and the check box \"can edit\" is not selected, other users can't update your files.\r\n\r\nactual behaviour:\r\nwhen you press share and the check box \"can edit\" is empty, users still can update your files and those updates are distributed between them.\r\n\r\nsteps to reproduce:\r\n1. make new folder\r\n2. share this folder - to a specific user or a group do not check \"can edit\"\r\n3. install owncloud client - windows or linux \r\n4. sync the share with another user who have access.\r\n5. on the client, who is not owner, touch a file from the folder or open it and save it without changes. this will change the time and date of the file.\r\n6. your update(file date and time) will be uploaded to the server folder and distributed to other clients, the result is a lot's of annoying update pop-ups.\r\n\r\n\r\nserver configuration:\r\nos:\r\ncentos release 6.3 (final) same effect on debian 6\r\nweb server:\r\nhttpd-2.2.15-15.el6.centos.1.x86_64\r\nor\r\napache2 i386 2.2.16-6+squeeze10\r\n\r\nphp version:\r\nphp-5.3.3-14.el6_3.x86_64\r\nor\r\nphp5 all 5.3.3-7+squeeze14 \r\n\r\nowncloud version: 4.5.6\r\n\r\nclient:\r\nowncloud-client 1.2.0-5\r\nowncloud-client 1.2.0 - for windows\r\n\r\nlog: it's very easy to reproduce if you need some specific log i will send it to you.\r\nthanks in advance good luck.\r\n","closed_by":{"login":"jancborchardt","id":925062,"avatar_url":"https://gravatar.com/avatar/2fd3f4d5d762955e5b603794a888fa97?d=https%3a%2f%2fidenticons.github.com%2f84ec51f9ceed468217d4e13abf78da9c.png&r=x","gravatar_id":"2fd3f4d5d762955e5b603794a888fa97","url":"https://api.github.com/users/jancborchardt","html_url":"https://github.com/jancborchardt","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jancborchardt/followers","following_url